Package fr.polytechtours.prd.multiagent.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Data to use for parameters
    In order to execute the algorithms, user should create this object by initializing all necessary parameters
    Job
    class Job: all informations associated with a job The start time, end time, a list of amounts for consuming the resources, which agent it belongs to, the weight and the factor for doing the sort
    Machine
    Class machine to store the resources of plate-form
    ParetoSolution
    This class is defined as the representation of one pareto solution
    Three elements are included in this class: sequence: list of ids of jobs which are able to be scheduled valueObjA: the value of the objective function for agent A valueObjB: the value of the objective function for agent B The order of domination is also defined by implementing the interface Comparable
    If one pareto solution dominates another one, the method compareTo return -1
    hashCode() and equals() are overrided.
